<template>
  <el-form :ref="name" :model="FormRes" inline :rules="FormData.Rules">
    <template v-for="item in FormData.Info">
      <el-form-item :key="item.prop" :prop="item.prop" :label="item.label">
        <el-input
          v-if="item.type === 'input'"
          v-model="FormRes[item.prop]"
          :type="item.ispass ? 'password' : ''"
        ></el-input>
      </el-form-item>
    </template>
  </el-form>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "formFinish",
  props:['name','FormRes','FormData'],
  data() {
    return {
      
    };
  },
};
</script>

<style></style>
